sections.text:
71-5803.15.Skilled nursing facility, defined.

Skilled nursing facility has the same meaning as in section 71-429.

SourceLaws 1979, LB 172, § 24;R.S.1943, (1996), § 71-5824;Laws 1997, LB 798, § 19;Laws 2000, LB 819, § 120.
